snippet.title: Amber Alert Arrest Connected to 2 Murders, Police Say | NBC10 Philadelphia
snippet.description:
A 2-year-old boy is safe after his father was taken into custody following an Amber Alert in Philadelphia. Police said the father is also a person of interest in the murders of the boy’s mother and grandmother. NBC10’s Aaron Baskerville has the details.
